    {
      "name": "📧 Email Management",
      "description": "Gmail থেকে client emails sync করা এবং lawyer থেকে client কে email পাঠানো।\n\n**Flow:**\n1. `POST /sync` → Gmail INBOX থেকে নতুন client emails DB তে save করো\n2. `POST /send` → Lawyer থেকে client কে reply করো (Gmail দিয়ে যাবে + DB তে save হবে)\n3. `GET /messages/:id` → একটি conversation-এর সব emails দেখো",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "POST /api/emails/sync — Gmail থেকে Emails আনো",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Sync successful', function () {",
                  "    pm.response.to.have.status(200);",
                  "    const json = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.expect(json.success).to.be.true;",
                  "    pm.expect(json).to.have.property('synced');",
                  "    console.log('Synced emails:', json.synced);",
                  "});"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/emails/sync",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "emails", "sync"]
            },
            "description": "Gmail INBOX থেকে নতুন (unread) client emails fetch করে MongoDB তে save করো।\n\n12-hour job automatically এটি করে। এটি হলো manual trigger।\n\n**Note:** GMAIL_APP_PASSWORD সঠিকভাবে .env তে দেওয়া থাকতে হবে।"
          },
          "response": [
            {
              "name": "New Emails Synced",
              "status": "OK",
              "code": 200,
              "body": "{\n  \"success\": true,\n  \"synced\": 3,\n  \"message\": \"3 new client email(s) synced from Gmail and saved to DB.\"\n}"
            },
            {
              "name": "No New Emails",
              "status": "OK",
              "code": 200,
              "body": "{\n  \"success\": true,\n  \"synced\": 0,\n  \"message\": \"0 new client email(s) synced from Gmail and saved to DB.\"\n}"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "POST /api/emails/send — Client কে Email পাঠাও",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Email sent successfully', function () {",
                  "    pm.response.to.have.status(200);",
                  "    const json = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.expect(json.success).to.be.true;",
                  "    if (json.conversationId) {",
                  "        pm.collectionVariables.set('conversationId', json.conversationId);",
                  "        console.log('conversationId saved:', json.conversationId);",
                  "    }",
                  "});"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"to\": \"{{clientEmail}}\",\n  \"subject\": \"Your Case Update — Hearing Date Confirmed\",\n  \"body\": \"Dear Client,\\n\\nI hope this email finds you well.\\n\\nYour case hearing has been scheduled for Monday, January 20th at 10:00 AM at the District Court.\\n\\nPlease bring the following documents:\\n1. National ID Card\\n2. Original contract agreement\\n3. Any receipts or payment proofs\\n\\nPlease be there 30 minutes early.\\n\\nBest regards,\\nRuhul (Advocate)\",\n  \"conversationId\": null\n}",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/emails/send",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "emails", "send"]
            },
            "description": "Lawyer থেকে Client কে email পাঠাও।\n\n- Email টি Gmail দিয়ে যাবে\n- DB তে `outgoing` message হিসেবে save হবে\n- `conversationId` দিলে existing conversation-এ add হবে, `null` দিলে নতুন conversation তৈরি হবে\n\n**Test script:** Response থেকে `conversationId` automatically collection variable-এ save হবে।"
          },
          "response": [
            {
              "name": "Email Sent Successfully",
              "status": "OK",
              "code": 200,
              "body": "{\n  \"success\": true,\n  \"message\": \"Email sent to client@gmail.com and saved to DB.\",\n  \"messageId\": \"<abc123@smtp.gmail.com>\",\n  \"conversationId\": \"65a1b2c3d4e5f6789012\"\n}"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "POST /api/emails/send — Reply to Existing Conversation",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"to\": \"{{clientEmail}}\",\n  \"subject\": \"Re: Your Legal Query\",\n  \"body\": \"Dear Client,\\n\\nThank you for your email.\\n\\nRegarding your question about the contract dispute, I have reviewed the documents you sent.\\n\\nWe will discuss this in detail at our next meeting.\\n\\nBest regards,\\nRuhul (Advocate)\",\n  \"conversationId\": \"{{conversationId}}\"\n}",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/emails/send",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "emails", "send"]
            },
            "description": "Existing conversation-এ reply করো। `conversationId` variable set থাকতে হবে।"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "GET /api/emails/messages/:id — Conversation Timeline দেখো",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Messages fetched', function () {",
                  "    pm.response.to.have.status(200);",
                  "    const json = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.expect(json.success).to.be.true;",
                  "    console.log('Total messages:', json.count);",
                  "});"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/emails/messages/{{conversationId}}",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "emails", "messages", "{{conversationId}}"]
            },
            "description": "একটি conversation-এর সব messages chronological order-এ দেখো (oldest first)।\n\nIncoming (client) ও outgoing (lawyer) দুটোই দেখাবে।"
          },
          "response": [
            {
              "name": "Messages List",
              "status": "OK",
              "code": 200,
              "body": "{\n  \"success\": true,\n  \"count\": 4,\n  \"messages\": [\n    {\n      \"_id\": \"65a1...\",\n      \"conversationId\": \"65a0...\",\n      \"sender\": \"client\",\n      \"senderEmail\": \"client@gmail.com\",\n      \"subject\": \"Contract Dispute Help\",\n      \"body\": \"I need help with my contract dispute...\",\n      \"direction\": \"incoming\",\n      \"isRead\": false,\n      \"createdAt\": \"2025-01-15T08:00:00Z\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"_id\": \"65a2...\",\n      \"sender\": \"lawyer\",\n      \"senderEmail\": \"ruhul@gmail.com\",\n      \"body\": \"Dear Client, I have reviewed your case...\",\n      \"direction\": \"outgoing\",\n      \"isRead\": true,\n      \"createdAt\": \"2025-01-15T09:30:00Z\"\n    }\n  ]\n}"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "🗂️ Conversations",
      "description": "Client-Lawyer conversation threads manage করো।\n\nপ্রতিটি conversation একজন client-এর সাথে সব emails-এর thread। প্রতিটি email sync বা send-এর সময় automatically conversation তৈরি বা update হয়।",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "GET /api/conversations — সব Conversations",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Conversations fetched', function () {",
                  "    pm.response.to.have.status(200);",
                  "    const json = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.expect(json.success).to.be.true;",
                  "    if (json.conversations && json.conversations.length > 0) {",
                  "        const firstId = json.conversations[0]._id;",
                  "        pm.collectionVariables.set('conversationId', firstId);",
                  "        console.log('First conversationId saved:', firstId);",
                  "    }",
                  "    console.log('Total conversations:', json.total);",
                  "});"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/conversations?status=active&page=1&limit=20",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "conversations"],
              "query": [
                { "key": "status", "value": "active", "description": "active | pending | closed (optional)" },
                { "key": "page", "value": "1", "description": "Page number" },
                { "key": "limit", "value": "20", "description": "Items per page" }
              ]
            },
            "description": "সব client conversations দেখো (সর্বশেষ email-এর conversation আগে)।\n\n**Test script:** প্রথম conversation-এর `_id` automatically `conversationId` variable-এ save হবে।\n\n**Query params:**\n- `status`: `active` | `pending` | `closed` (না দিলে সব দেখাবে)\n- `page`: page number (default: 1)\n- `limit`: প্রতি page-এ কতটা (default: 20)"
          },
          "response": [
            {
              "name": "Conversations List",
              "status": "OK",
              "code": 200,
              "body": "{\n  \"success\": true,\n  \"total\": 5,\n  \"page\": 1,\n  \"conversations\": [\n    {\n      \"_id\": \"65a1b2c3d4e5f6789012\",\n      \"subject\": \"Contract Dispute Help\",\n      \"clientEmail\": \"rahim@gmail.com\",\n      \"clientName\": \"Rahim Uddin\",\n      \"lawyerEmail\": \"ruhul@gmail.com\",\n      \"status\": \"active\",\n      \"messageCount\": 8,\n      \"lastMessageAt\": \"2025-01-15T09:00:00Z\",\n      \"createdAt\": \"2025-01-10T08:00:00Z\"\n    }\n  ]\n}"
            }
          ]
        },
